-- Haniel Shortlists Three CEO Candidates, FT Deutschland Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-02-23T19:22:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-23/haniel-shortlists-three-ceo-candidates-ft-deutschland-reports.html
Franz Haniel & Cie GmbH has
shortlisted three external candidates in its search for a
successor to Chief Executive Officer Juergen Kluge,  Financial
Times Deutschland  said in a preview of a story that will run
tomorrow, citing an unidentified spokesperson for the German
company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  